 the character currently doing an action that has the potential of failing? For example, jumping over a big hole or using its strength to move something incredibly heavy or trying to heal someone or trying to recall how to perform in an aristocratic context or trying to keep their balance, etc.\r\n```\r\n\r\nYour reply must be structured into a strict JSON representing the following:\r\n```interface Response\r\n{\r\n  listOfCharactersByName: string[];\r\n  actions: CharacterAction;\r\n}\r\n\r\ninterface CharacterAction\r\n{\r\n  characterName: string;\r\n  actionCategory: string;\r\n  bonus: int;\r\n  charactersWhoCanResist: string[];\r\n  reasoning: string;\r\n}```.\r\n\r\ncharacterName represents the name of the character initiating the action. actionCategory represents one of the actionCategories listed below. charactersWhoCanResist represents the characters in the scene that have a chance to resist this particular action.\r\n\r\nYour categorization options are:\r\n<actionCategories>\r\nSex\r\nAcrobatics\r\nAthletics\r\nDeception\r\nCharisma\r\nIntimidation\r\nMedicine\r\nPerformance\r\nSociety\r\nAristocracy\r\nStealth\r\nThievery\r\n</actionCategories>\r\n\r\nOnly include actions based on your omniscient truth. For example, a character that is telling the truth won't trigger a Deception action even if another character think that they are hiding something. To help you choose the right actionCategories, here is a description of each of them:\r\n- Sex is about sexual knowledge, sexual acts performance, sexual teasing, sensuality, etc). Other characters can't resist Sex action category. The roll represents how well the sex action is performed.\r\n  *Examples*\r\n  *A character giving a handjob.\r\n  *A character giving a blowjob(fellatio).\r\n  *A character dancing sensually.\r\n  *A character seducing another character.\r\n  *A character having sex with another character.\r\n  *A character involved in a sexual situation.\r\n  *A character discussing kinks.\r\n- Acrobatics is when someone is dodging or doing acrobatic movements or using their agility to critically enhance their movements.\r\n  *Examples*\r\n  *A character is dodging an attack.\r\n  *A character is using their reflex to avoid an impact.\r\n  *A character is doing acrobatic movements such as flip, twist, dance or any other movement requiring good balance.\r\n- Athletics is about physical strength.\r\n  *Examples*\r\n  *A character is using their strength to move an object.\r\n  *A character is pushing or shoving someone or something.\r\n  *A character is pulling hard on someone or something.\r\n  *A character is restraining someone physically.\r\n- Deception is when someone is lying, when they're being misleading, dishonest or insincere. Someone resisting the deception will be aware or suspicious that the other person lied.\r\n  *Examples*\r\n  *A character is lying to someone.\r\n  *A character is giving fake information to someone.\r\n- Charisma is about diplomacy, argumentation, debating and persuasion. Someone resisting the charisma check will be unswayed or notice the attempt of the other person.\r\n  *Examples*\r\n  *A character is trying to persuade someone.\r\n  *A character is arguing with someone.\r\n- Intimidation is when someone is intimidating someone else by using physical strength, coercion, compulsion, oppression, harassment, threats or by using their influence. Someone influenced by the intimidation check (failing their roll) may not comply directly, but they'll be intimidated nonetheless.\r\n  *Examples*\r\n  *A character is threatening someone.\r\n  *A character is using their physical strength to constrains or restrain someone else.\r\n  *A character is oppressing or harassing someone.\r\n  *A character is using their influence to coerce someone.\r\n- Medicine is when someone is using medicinal knowledge to treat a condition or to get insights. Medical acts are also included in this category. People can't resist a Medicine check.\r\n  *Examples*\r\n  *A character is analyzing a medical condition.\r\n  *A character is treating the wound of someone.\r\n  *A character is preparing a medicinal mixture or potion.\r\n- Performance is when someone is acting, masking their emotions or disguising themselves. Someone resisting the performance check will notice the fakeness, fraud or trickery behind it.\r\n  *Examples*\r\n  *A character is acting as someone else.\r\n  *A character is masking their emotions under a mask of indifference.\r\n  *A character is talking in front of a crowd.\r\n- Society is when someone is using their knowledge about politics or how society works. Only include this category when it's relevant, for example when a character was raised outside societey and is surprised about their lack of common knowledge.\r\n  *Examples*\r\n  *A character who was born and raised in a forest is surprised by how society work.\r\n*A character is discussing political context.\r\n- Aristocracy is when a character is using manners or etiquette, usually in nobility or aristocratic context. Elitism knowledge.\r\n  *Examples*\r\n  *A character is attending a dinner in a noble or aristocratic household.\r\n  *A character is discussing about a noble or aristocratic family.\r\n  *A character is discussing about privileged information accessible by elites.\r\n- Stealth is when a character is trying to not be perceived by another. When they're trying to dissimulate or conceal themselves.\r\n  *Examples*\r\n  * Someone trying to catch a glimpse of a woman breasts without her noticing.\r\n  *A character is hiding their presence from others.\r\n  *A character is hiding themselves in the shadows.\r\n  *A character is trying not ot be noticed.\r\n- Thievery is when a character is stealing or trying to steal, including sleigh of hand.\r\n  *Examples*\r\n  *A character is stealing something from another character.\r\n\r\nHere are some examples of scenes you previously analyzed correctly:\r\n<examples>\r\n```\r\n<messages_for_context_on_scene>\r\n<message>Aria sat patiently at her desk a few minutes after her class ended, waiting for her friend to return. After a few more minutes, Aria looked around noticing she was the only one there, getting excited as she realized that she would be alone with the new sexy teacher. She straightened her uniform as she remained seated as still as she could.\r\n\r\nHer head turned to the front desk where the teacher, Marius, sat.\r\n\r\n\"Hello sir, I know you said the extra class was cancelled but I'm hoping there's still something I could work on for some credits.\" she said cutely.</message>\r\n</messages_for_context_on_scene>\r\n<scene_to_categorize><message>I raised my eyes to hers.\r\n\"Oh, hello miss, I didn't see you there. A task that you could do for points? What exactly did you have in mind?\" I asked curiously as my eyes went to her breasts, before going back up to her eyes.</message></scene_to_categorize>\r\n\r\nYour correct response:\r\n<response>\r\n  {\r\n    \"listOfCharactersByName\": [\r\n      \"Aria\",\r\n      \"Marius\"\r\n    ],\r\n    \"actions\": [\r\n\t  {\r\n        \"characterName\": \"Aria\",\r\n        \"actionCategory\": \"Charisma\",\r\n\t\t\"charactersWhoCanResist\": [\r\n\t\t  \"Marius\"\r\n\t\t],\r\n\t\t\"bonus\": 2,\r\n        \"reasoning\": \"Aria is using her cuteness to convince Marius to give her a task to earn credits.\"\r\n      },\r\n      {\r\n        \"characterName\": \"Marius\",\r\n        \"actionCategory\": \"Stealth\",\r\n\t\t\"charactersWhoCanResist\": [\r\n\t\t  \"Aria\"\r\n\t\t],\r\n\t\t\"bonus\": 0,\r\n        \"reasoning\": \"Marius is looking at Aria's breasts. He is trying to be subtle.\"\r\n      }\r\n    ]\r\n  }\r\n</response>\r\n```\r\nBonus is 2 since Marius is receptive to Aria's cuteness (looking at breasts).\r\n\r\n```\r\n<messages_for_context_on_scene>\r\n<message>I stopped in front of the bedroom door, a girl blocking my path.\r\n\r\n\"Move, I need to go inside\" I said.</message></messages_for_context_on_scene>\r\n<scene_to_categorize><message>Marie looked at him right in the eyes.\r\n\"You don't know who you're talking to, peasant, do you?\" she asked arrogantly.\r\n\r\nShe crossed her arms, a knowning smirk appeared on her lips.\r\n\r\n\"I am the princess. So you should refer to me with respect, Eric.\" She lied.</message></scene_to_categorize>\r\n\r\nYour correct response:\r\n<response>\r\n  {\r\n    \"listOfCharactersByName\": [\r\n      \"Marie\",\r\n      \"Eric\"\r\n    ],\r\n    \"actions\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"characterName\": \"Marie\",\r\n        \"actionCategory\": \"Deception\",\r\n\t\t\"charactersWhoCanResist\": [\r\n\t\t  \"Marius\"\r\n\t\t],\r\n\t\t\"bonus\": 0,\r\n        \"reasoning\": \"Marie is lying to Marius.\"\r\n      },\r\n      {\r\n        \"characterName\": \"Marie\",\r\n        \"actionCategory\": \"Charisma\",\r\n\t\t\"charactersWhoCanResist\": [\r\n\t\t  \"Marius\"\r\n\t\t],\r\n\t\t\"bonus\": 0,\r\n        \"reasoning\": \"Marie is trying to persuade Marius that she is a princess.\"\r\n      },\r\n      {\r\n        \"characterName\": \"Marie\",\r\n        \"actionCategory\": \"Performance\",\r\n\t\t\"charactersWhoCanResist\": [\r\n\t\t  \"Marius\"\r\n\t\t],\r\n\t\t\"bonus\": 0,\r\n        \"reasoning\": \"Marie is acting as if she is a princess.\"\r\n      }\r\n    ]\r\n  }\r\n</response>\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n<messages_for_context_on_scene>\r\n<message>\"So, why are you trying to bully me?\" I asked with a frown.</message>\r\n<message>Roger had a smirk on his lips whilst Yterion crossed his arms.\r\n\r\n\"Bully you? Oh Thorin, You think you're worth the effort?\" He asked.</message>\r\n<message>I threw a rock towards Kikono.</message>\r\n<message>Roger dodged easily the rock, the smirk on his lips only growing.\r\n\r\n\"You're clearly not good enough to even throw rocks\" He said.</message>\r\n<message>\"Just stop dodging already, asshole!\" I yelled.</message></messages_for_context_on_scene>\r\n<scene_to_categorize><message>Roger picked up a rock from the ground and threw it straight at my face.\r\n\r\n\"If you can do it, don't think I can't!\" He said.</message></scene_to_categorize>\r\n\r\nYour correct response:\r\n<response>\r\n  {\r\n    \"listOfCharactersByName\": [\r\n      \"Roger\",\r\n      \"Yterion\",\r\n      \"Thorin\"\r\n    ],\r\n    \"actions\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"characterName\": \"Thorin\",\r\n        \"actionCategory\": \"Acrobatics\",\r\n\t\t\"charactersWhoCanResist\": [\r\n\t\t  \"Thorin\"\r\n\t\t],\r\n\t\t\"bonus\": 0,\r\n        \"reasoning\": \"Roger is throwing a rock at Thorin. Thorin will most likely try to dodge.\"\r\n      }\r\n    ]\r\n  }\r\n</response>\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n<messages_for_context_on_scene>\r\n<message>I looked at her perfectly round breasts with hunger.\r\n\r\n\"You're so beautiful, Lilia\" I said with heavy breath.</message>\r\n<message>Lilia smirked before she put your dick in her small mouth, teasing the tip playfully.\r\n\r\n\"You're not ready for tonight, Hyjal\" She said.</message>\r\n<message>I grunted.\r\n\r\n\"Please stop teasing, put it in your mouth entirely\" I begged.</message></messages_for_context_on_scene>\r\n<scene_to_categorize><message>Lilia grinned, but kept teasing the tip with her fluttering tongue.\r\n\r\n\"How about you tell me how wonderful I am and maybe I'll entertain you\" She asked.\r\n\r\nHer hand went to your chest, scratching gently.</message></scene_to_categorize>\r\n\r\nYour correct response:\r\n<response>\r\n  {\r\n    \"listOfCharactersByName\": [\r\n      \"Lilia\",\r\n      \"Hyjal\"\r\n    ],\r\n    \"actions\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"characterName\": \"Lilia\",\r\n        \"actionCategory\": \"Sex\",\r\n\t\t\"charactersWhoCanResist\": [],\r\n\t\t\"bonus\": 0,\r\n        \"reasoning\": \"Lilia is giving a teasing blowjob.\"\r\n      },\r\n      {\r\n        \"characterName\": \"Lilia\",\r\n        \"actionCategory\": \"Charisma\",\r\n\t\t\"charactersWhoCanResist\": [\r\n\t\t  \"Hyjal\"\r\n\t\t],\r\n\t\t\"bonus\": 4,\r\n        \"reasoning\": \"Lilia is trying to persuade someone to give her compliments.\"\r\n      }\r\n    ]\r\n  }\r\n</response>\r\n```\r\n\r\nA few precision on these examples:\r\n\r\nLilia has a +4 bonus on her charisma in the scene since Hyjal is already under her charm. Thorin is not the one throwing the rock, but he has an acrobatic ability check since he's trying to *dodge* the rock.\r\n\r\n</examples>\r\n Please note that you should only include categorization of actions that *MATTERS* against other characters in the context. Only include *RELEVANT* categories, do NOT include irrelevant ones. Ignore mundane actions taken by characters, those always succeed. Only list actions that may be resisted by other characters (attacking,escaping perception,convincing,intimidating,etc).\r\n</task>",
